ease date for highly-anticipated Squid Game season 2.\", \"from\": 6903, \"to\": 7001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6918, \"end\": 6926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Yoo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gong Yoo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Yoo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gong_Yoo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Continue to read on and catch up on such exciting K-drama and K-pop updates from this week.\", \"from\": 7002, \"to\": 7093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 2, many reports emerged stating thatBTS member Jinwill participate in the torch relay at the Paris Olympics 2024, representing his country South Korea.\", \"from\": 7095, \"to\": 7254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7242, \"end\": 7253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.991306875394151e-24, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after, the group's agency HYBE stated that they would confirm further after a thorough consultation with the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 7255, \"to\": 7404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7372, \"end\": 7403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans did not have to wait longer for the confirmation.\", \"from\": 7406, \"to\": 7460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 3, the agency officially announced that Jin will become South Korea's torchbearer at the 2024 Paris Olympics, which is scheduled to commence on July 26.\", \"from\": 7461, \"to\": 7621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7509, \"end\": 7512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0622977043212136e-11, \"text\": \"Jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Seok-jin\"}, {\"begin\": 7525, \"end\": 7536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.991306875394151e-24, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the exact date and time of his participation in the traditional toch really will be revealed later.\", \"from\": 7622, \"to\": 7730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ryan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman are currently in South Korea to promote their upcoming film Deadpool & Wolverine.\", \"from\": 7732, \"to\": 7844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7732, \"end\": 7745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Reynolds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4901109025992292e-88, \"text\": \"Ryan Reynolds\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Reynolds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Reynolds\"}, {\"begin\": 7750, \"end\": 7762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Jackman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hugh Jackman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Jackman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hugh_Jackman\"}, {\"begin\": 7780, \"end\": 7791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.991306875394151e-24, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedi